  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-tool=\"markdown编辑器\" data-website=\"https://markdown.com.cn/editor\" style=\"font-size: 16px;word-spacing: 0px;letter-spacing: 0px;word-break: break-word;word-wrap: break-word;text-align: justify;margin-top: -10px;line-height: 1.75;color: #595959;font-family: SimHei, Arial;background-size: 20px 20px;background-position: center center;padding: 2px 12px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">上个月，Google 正式发布了专业级 AI 图像生成与编辑模型 ——&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Nano Banana Pro</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它带来了</span><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">完美的文字渲染</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">、</span><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">多图融合一致性</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">以及</span><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">原生 4K 分辨率</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">支持。这意味着，AI 图像生成不再仅仅是创意探索的玩具，而是正式具备了接入企业级生产环境的能力。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然 banana 在多个生图场景表现优异，但对打工人而言，其最大的价值在于</span><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">信息可视化</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。它能够显著提升高质量图表、PPT 及文章配图的效率。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文将探讨 Nano Banana Pro 还能应用到哪些办公场景，分享写更稳定提示词的技巧。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(222, 198, 251);color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\"><span leaf=\"\">一. 应用场景</span></span></h3>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 文章摘要</span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">工作中进行产品调研或阅读大量文章时，纯文本摘要往往难以形成直观记忆，可以让 banana 生成文章摘要：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">以黑板风格、手写体的外观总结内容，并像老师写的一样，用图表和易于理解的表达方式进行分解，同时使用颜色。文章：&lt;文章链接/内容&gt;</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016832\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px 0px #eee;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3229e52d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4Hagy3EwFLmVrEBR4CVATUwKicp6bLOnXButqGZ6vxU2TSXbKp20txhMlU5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016830\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px 0px #eee;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05ff833f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4Hagyzib5ILN6iaNiaZcmX5sabOZiaSbBGh4I8OiccHNBkX8mujZZFzCbCwuCajg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016833\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px 0px #eee;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29cf3f76&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4HagyLsibjPc1hHaGSQhtic43iaHBQRbXyiaEiaibX2DeQr0siaUcHI2WxNF5mVj0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 科研绘图</span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">画技术架构图、时序图费时费力，可以通过自然语言描述业务逻辑，画出稳定好看的科研绘图：</span></p>\n   <summary><span leaf=\"\">科研绘图提示词</span></summary>\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">You are a specialized UI/UX designer creating diagrams for modern technical documentation (like Notion docs, SaaS whitepapers, or Engineering Wikis). Create a clean,&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Modern Flat Vector Flowchart</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;based on the workflow description provided below.</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Visual Style &amp; Aesthetic</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Style:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Minimalist, flat vector art. Friendly and corporate-clean</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Approach:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">No academic stiffness, no complex 3D elements, no photorealism</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Line Style:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Smooth, uniform lines</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Corner Style</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Rounded corners for all rectangles and paths (modern, approachable look)</span></span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Morandi Color Palette (Soft &amp; Professional)</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Background:&nbsp;</span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Clean White (</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjfthxr-62fnp6\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#FFFFFF</a></span></code><span leaf=\"\">)&nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Extremely faint warm grey (</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjfthxr-f0ss6m\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#F9F9F9</a></span></code><span leaf=\"\">)</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Process Nodes</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;</span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Muted Slate Blue (</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjfthxs-gawpxu\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#B0C4DE</a></span></code><span leaf=\"\">)&nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Dusty Blue-Grey</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Decision/Warning Nodes</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;</span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Muted Sand/Ochre (</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjfthxs-lwkkdn\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#EEDC82</a></span></code><span leaf=\"\">)&nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Soft Earthy Orange</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Start/End/Success Nodes</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;</span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Sage Green (</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjfthxs-vpxot2\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#8FBC8F</a></span></code><span leaf=\"\">)&nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Desaturated Mint</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Connectors</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;</span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Dark Grey (</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27,31,35,.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjfthxs-1wgik8\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#555555</a></span></code><span leaf=\"\">) - not pitch black</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Node &amp; Shape Specifications (Role-Based)</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Start/End</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Pill shapes (fully rounded ends)</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Operations/Steps</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Rounded rectangles (border radius ~10px) - simple and clean</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Decisions</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Diamonds with slightly rounded corners</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Connectors</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Clean elbow lines (90-degree turns) with subtle, simple arrowheads</span></span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Layout Guidelines</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Structure:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Strictly aligned to a grid</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Flow Direction</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Top-to-Bottom OR Left-to-Right (select based on content)</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Spacing</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">High whitespace usage - diagram should feel 'breathable' and easy to scan</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Clarity</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Spacious layout for optimal readability</span></span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Rendering Details</span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Text</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Minimal abstract lines or clean Sans-Serif font style</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Quality Standard</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Should look like a high-quality export from Figma, Whimsical, or Lucidchart</span></span></strong></li>\n    <li><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Overall Vibe</span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Professional, modern, and accessible for technical documentation</span></span></strong></li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Use Cases</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Perfect for:</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Notion documentation</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">SaaS whitepapers</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Engineering wikis</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Technical process documentation</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Modern corporate presentations</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100016843\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f6d8c84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4Hagy58z0TlPqq3xVticeLibnF8cP4PA7Ya4ibn9RAhM1e2HH2ZWmcNAypvficw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016844\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7badd3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4HagynwOnNiabaOj17ibM5UlicnJtDicS125o0P004y6sZ9LdYCmEmq993gaXtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100016845\" data-ratio=\"0.7462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ff59bf7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4Hagy7SRol56iboLyiaf9GTRDy1z5n24gVaXWRVjjJgTOXRvmBxp5KO8ZXnkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h4 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. PPT</span></h4>\n   <p data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">年终总结、项目复盘，生成多种风格的 PPT</span></p>\n   <summary><span leaf=\"\">3D 玻璃拟态风格 PPT</span></summary>\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你是一位专家级UI UX演示设计师，请生成高保真、未来科技感的16比9演示文稿幻灯片。请根据视觉平衡美学，自动在封面、网格布局或数据可视化中选择一种最完美的构图。&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">全局视觉语言方面，风格要无缝融合Apple Keynote的极简主义、现代SaaS产品设计和玻璃拟态风格。整体氛围需要高端、沉浸、洁净且有呼吸感。光照采用电影级体积光、柔和的光线追踪反射和环境光遮蔽。配色方案选择深邃的虚空黑或纯净的陶瓷白作为基底，并以流动的极光渐变色即霓虹紫、电光蓝、柔和珊瑚橙、青色作为背景和UI高光点缀。 关于画面内容模块，请智能整合以下元素： 1. 排版引擎采用Bento便当盒网格系统，将内容组织在模块化的圆角矩形容器中。容器材质必须是带有模糊效果的磨砂玻璃，具有精致的白色边缘和柔和的投影，并强制保留巨大的内部留白，避免拥挤。 2. 插入礼物质感的3D物体，渲染独特的高端抽象3D制品作为视觉锚点。它们的外观应像实体的昂贵礼物或收藏品，材质为抛光金属、幻彩亚克力、透明玻璃或软硅胶，形状可能是 3D 可视化图表或 3D 信息图。 3. 字体与数据方面，使用干净的无衬线字体，建立高对比度。如果有图表，请使用发光的3D饼图、时间线或悬浮数字，图表应看起来像发光的霓虹灯玩具。 构图逻辑参考： 如果生成封面，请在中心放置一个巨大的复杂3D玻璃物体，并覆盖粗体大字，背景有延伸的极光波浪。 如果生成内容页，请使用Bento网格布局，将3D图标放在小卡片中，文本放在大卡片中。 如果生成数据页，请使用分屏设计，左侧排版文字，右侧悬浮巨大的发光3D数据可视化图表。 渲染质量要求：虚幻引擎5渲染，8k分辨率，超细节纹理，UI设计感，UX界面，Dribbble热门趋势，设计奖获奖作品。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100016846\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d14c5375&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbwggjczjMMLvVzz7vvwtSfCw6Zf4HagyWMnbiaib2kDrXpCjgUtMmqdwY4gHR9XjZ1FqUtic0OjsaxodSkDlwFDbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016848\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=